org.openimaj.util.pair

Class IndependentPair<A,B>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.util.pair.IndependentPair<A,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the class of the first object in the pair
    B - the class of the second object in the pair
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Pair, ReadWritableIndependentPair

    public class IndependentPair<A,B>
extends Object
    IndependentPair represents a generic pair of objects of different (independent) types.

    Jonathon Hare
